racy was facing during this turbulent period of European feudalism.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aLiterary Studies -- General Criticism and Theory. 7aPOETRY / European / General.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476472840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804764728423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804764728/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles